messages.title: It's Official!
messages.content: Voting Labour here only helps him win
Your vote will make the difference...

mentions.tacticalSituation: Labour finished fourth in the 2019 European Elections. Labour have never won in Altrincham & Sale West. Voting Labour in Altrincham & Sale West splits the anti-Tory Remain vote and risks letting Boris Johnson's candidate win.

issues.brexitEurope: "The Lib Dems are unequivocal remainers who want to stop Brexit from happening." - The Guardian

endorsements.endorsement: Recommending you vote Liberal Democrat in Altrincham & Sale West.

images.caption: The Guardian quote about Liberal Democrats' position on Brexit.
